{
  "chapter": 309,
  "chapter_summary": "本章分三条线并行展开。寇仲随宋鲁、宋智抵达宋家山城，被告知宋缺已将他名字刻在磨刀石上，随时可能取他性命，但寇仲毫不畏惧，毅然前往磨刀堂面见宋缺。宋缺冷冷指出他来迟至少一年，二人首次会面充满张力。与此同时，徐子陵化名弓辰春在乌江帮与四川合一派的夏妙莹、丝娜展开三招之约。他借林朗佩刀，以长生诀寒热劲气和血战十式巧妙取胜，给足对方面子后握手言和。事后雷九指追入舱房，揭露自己是鲁妙子未正式承认的弟子，凭一对特训耳朵识破徐子陵戴面具伪装。雷九指讲述三十多年前跟随鲁妙子学赌的经历，鲁妙子传他戒贪二字诀，二人由此结下师徒缘份。徐子陵告知鲁妙子已仙逝，雷九指闻讯泪流满面。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋智",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "我两人应否陪少帅一起进去见大兄呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_song_zhi",
      "text": "听你这么说，大兄应该是指定要单独会见小仲。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "鲁叔和智叔是否怕阀主拿我来试刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋智",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "试你的刀法是必然的事。问题是他会不会下手杀你。照惯例给他把名字刻在磨刀石的人，最终都会命丧于他刀下。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_zhi",
      "text": "他为何忽然要杀我，杀我对他老人家有甚么好处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋智",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "大兄从来行事敦人难以测度，前一阵子他暗下离开山城，回来后就把你的名字刻在磨刀石上。我曾多次试探，他都不肯透露半点口风，所以此事只能赌你的运气，若少帅立即离城，我们绝不会怪你。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "我寇仲岂是临阵退缩的人，我更有把握可活着出来找两位喝酒呢。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_xia_miao_ying",
      "text": "姥姥请勿误会，我只是看看可否找人借刀子一用。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_lang",
      "speaker_name": "林朗",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "弓爷看看这把是否合用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_huo_ji_tong",
      "text": "无论事情如何发展，我和你们的事与乌江帮绝没有任何关系。假若我弓辰春落败遭擒，当然没资格说话。但如果弓某人侥幸取胜，而霍纪童你却在事后寻乌江帮的麻烦，我弓辰舂于此立下誓言，不论事情大小，必取尔之命。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_miao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "夏妙莹",
      "listener": "char_si_na",
      "text": "娜儿退下！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_na",
      "speaker_name": "丝娜",
      "listener": "char_xia_miao_ying",
      "text": "师傅放心！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_xia_miao_ying",
      "text": "此战作和论，弓某人根本没有把握在三招内胜过丝娜当家，只是利用潜隐多年悟出来的小玩意兵行险着，是否仍要打下去，姥姥一言可决。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_miao_ying",
      "speaker_name": "夏妙莹",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "败就是败，不用你来为我们说好话，我们走。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_que",
      "text": "后辈寇仲，拜见阀主！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_que",
      "speaker_name": "宋缺",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你来迟啦！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_que",
      "text": "我来迟了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_que",
      "speaker_name": "宋缺",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你来迟至少一年。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "你跟来作甚么？",
      "tone": "不满",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "当然是有要事商量。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "我和你以前没有任何关系，以后也不会有。识相的就给我滚出去，否则莫怪弓某人不客气。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "弓兄勿要唬我，你这人外冷内热，更非恃强凌弱之徒，只要你肯听我几句话，保证会对小弟改观过来。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "你先答我，刚才你为何要强出头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "因为你戴着我恩师亲制的面具。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "雷兄确是眼力高明，不知你所说的恩师高姓大名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我虽视鲁妙子大师为师，他却从不肯承认我是他的徒弟。但我雷九指之所以有今天的成就，全拜他所赐。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "你甚么时候看破我戴面具的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我只是猜出来的。我一对耳朵受过特别的锻练，不但能听到盅内骰子转动时声音上的微妙差别，更可在远距离窃听别人的说话。当我发觉你竟不知夏妙莹是冲着你来峙，便猜到你非是真正的弓辰春，而事实上你比弓辰春要高明百倍。所以我故意走到你背后，留心观察颈肤和面肤的分别，始肯定你是戴上面具。亦只有出自鲁师妙手的脸具，才能如此全无破绽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "鲁先生既从不认你为徒，那你跟鲁先生究竟是甚么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "那是三十多年前的事，我当时只有十五岁，在关中一所赌场当跑腿，有一天鲁妙子来赌钱，以无可比拟的赌术狠狠赢了一笔钱。他离开时我追在他身后，恳求他把嬴钱的手法教我，唉！当时我还以为他只是个手法比人高明的赌徒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "他怎么说？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "他赏我一记耳光，然后大笑道：急功近利，想以骗人技俩一朝致富的人，永远成不了赌林高手，我既打过你，就传你两字诀法吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "是那两个字。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "就是戒贪两字。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "鲁先生真绝。你还有甚么话可说？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我当时哑口无言，鲁师却续道：凭我的赌术，可轻易把这样一个赌场赢过来。但我只嬴五十两便离场，这就是戒贪。只有能完全控制自己贪喷痴的人，才有资格去赢别人的钱，所以我绝非胡诌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "雷九指",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "当我以为鲁师会舍我而去时，忽然他又走过来摸摸我的头，喃喃自语的道：你这小子有副很不错的头骨，眼也生得精灵，横竖我正要一个助手，你就跟我一段时间吧。事情就是那么开始的。那是我一生人最快乐的时光，他从不教我任何东西，却不阻我在旁偷看偷学。可惜只有短短半年时间。他老人家好吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "弓辰春",
      "listener": "char_lei_jiu_zhi",
      "text": "鲁先生早已仙去。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 309,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    }
  ],
